## User Language Preference Management

### Korean-First User Entity
- **Default Language**: Korean (ko-KR)
- **Default Timezone**: Asia/Seoul
- **Default Date Format**: yyyy년 MM월 dd일
- **Default Time Format**: 24시간 형식
- **Default Currency**: KRW (Korean Won)

### Language Preference API Endpoints
```
GET    /api/user/preferences/language     - Get user's language preference
PUT    /api/user/preferences/language     - Update user's language preference
GET    /api/user/preferences/locale       - Get complete locale settings
PUT    /api/user/preferences/locale       - Update locale settings
GET    /api/supported-languages           - Get list of supported languages
```

